last_episode_to_air.overview: Cal works with Maggie as she fights to save the Crossing, while a careless mistake may cost someone their life.

name: Sullivan's Crossing
overview: After Neurosurgeon Maggie Sullivan’s personal and professional life are thrown into turmoil she returns home to Sullivan’s Crossing. While there, Maggie is forced to navigate her complicated present while confronting the painful past she has chosen to ignore for years.

episodes.name: Coming Home
episodes.overview: When neurosurgeon Maggie Sullivan's seemingly perfect life in Boston is turned upside down, she leaves the city and her boyfriend, Andrew, to return to her childhood home of Sullivan's Crossing in Nova Scotia.

episodes.name: Homewrecker
episodes.overview: Maggie sees Cal in a new light after they help an injured resident and spend time together at karaoke.

episodes.name: Detours
episodes.overview: Sydney attempts to cheer up Maggie after she suffers a setback back at home. Frank and Edna help Sully, with the annual land blessing, but the festivities end early after a camper goes missing. Maggie and Cal work together with the search and rescue team unaware that another life hangs in the balance.

episodes.name: Rock and a Hard Place
episodes.overview: Maggie and Cal work against the clock in a daring medical rescue, and in the process discover a clue to the whereabouts of a missing camper. Maggie learns a little more about Cal’s past, while Sully receives disturbing news.

episodes.name: Pressure Drop
episodes.overview: Maggie makes a difficult decision after Sully lets his temper get the best of him.

episodes.name: Boiling Point
episodes.overview: Sully tries to hold things together at Sullivan's Crossing, while Maggie attempts to navigate complications back in Boston, Mass.

episodes.name: Second Chances
episodes.overview: Tensions escalate as Maggie returns to Sullivan's Crossing with Andrew.

episodes.name: Aftershock
episodes.overview: Maggie struggles to make sense of her personal life. Sully deals with some financial challenges.

episodes.name: Can't Help Falling
episodes.overview: Maggie's medical training is put to the test as she races against the clock to save the life of a friend.

episodes.name: Sins of the Father
episodes.overview: Maggie returns to Boston prepared to face the consequences of her actions, while Cal searches for closure of his own.

episodes.name: Guilt Trip
episodes.overview: Maggie Sullivan returns to the Crossing to find Sully in the hospital, struggling with the feeling that he's forgotten something; Cal Jones is confused when Maggie gives him the cold shoulder, unaware that Lola pocketed his goodbye letter.

episodes.name: A Storm Is Brewing
episodes.overview: Maggie searches for clues regarding the cause of Sully's condition as she struggles to make a decision about her own future.

episodes.name: Confessions
episodes.overview: Maggie, Cal, Lola, and Sydney help Edna prepare the campground for a storm as Frank helps Sully to figure out what's been eating at him.

episodes.name: Eye of the Storm
episodes.overview: Things start to heat up between Maggie and Cal when they're forced to take shelter at Cal's cabin.

episodes.name: Secrets
episodes.overview: Uncertain about her own future as well as that of the Crossing, Maggie tries to find a way to help Sully.

episodes.name: Revelations
episodes.overview: Maggie's world is turned upside down after she learns some devastating news about her stepfather.

episodes.name: Reunions
episodes.overview: Reeling over the news of Maggie's pregnancy, Cal receives a visitor; Phoebe and Sully start to bond over the idea of being grandparents.

episodes.name: Truth and Consequences
episodes.overview: Maggie helps care for Cal's sister and in the process learns more about his past.

episodes.name: Remorse
episodes.overview: Maggie enlists Cal’s help when Sully becomes convinced he needs to take drastic measures to make amends with Lola.

episodes.name: It's a Wonderful Life
episodes.overview: Cal works with Maggie as she fights to save the Crossing, while a careless mistake may cost someone their life.
